== 飞行学校 ==
2007年11月，区域快线航空公司和[[芒格洛尔机场|芒格洛尔机场]]有限公司联合创建了一个飞行员学院，校名为民用航空训练学院（Civil Aviation Training Academy），地点位于[[维多利亚州|维多利亚州]]的芒格洛尔机场。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.regionalexpress.com/corp_info/ShowNews.aspx?nid=157&page=MC |title=Rex and Mangalore Airport Announce Creation of Pilot Academy |accessdate=2009-03-08 |archive-date=2008-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080723191058/https://www.regionalexpress.com/corp_info/ShowNews.aspx?nid=157&page=MC |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年4月，区域快线买下了学院的全部所有权，并将其更名为澳大利亚航空飞行员学院（Australian Airline Pilot Academy）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.regionalexpress.com.au/corp_info/ShowNews.aspx?nid=177&page=MC |title=Rex fully acquires pilot training academy |accessdate=2009-03-08 |archive-date=2009-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090916120957/http://regionalexpress.com.au/corp_info/ShowNews.aspx?nid=177&page=MC |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2009年2月18日，区域快线宣布澳大利亚航空飞行员学院将于2009年4月起与沃加沃加市合作，并从芒格洛尔机场迁至沃加沃加机场<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.weeklytimesnow.com.au/article/2009/02/18/54931_latest-news.html |title=REX to relocate pilot academy |accessdate=2009-03-08 |archive-date=2009-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090315002934/http://www.weeklytimesnow.com.au/article/2009/02/18/54931_latest-news.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.regionalexpress.com.au/corp_info/ShowNews.aspx?nid=202&page=MC |title=REX TO CONSTRUCT PILOT ACADEMY AT WAGGA WAGGA |accessdate=2009-03-08 |archive-date=2009-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091026075949/http://www.regionalexpress.com.au//corp_info/ShowNews.aspx?nid=202&page=MC |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

